"title": "5307: envoy",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5307: envoy",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An official representative sent on behalf of a king or government to other kings or nations. Believers are God's envoys to his world, bearing the good news of salvation on his behalf.</p>\n<h2>Envoys sent to other kings or governments</h2>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:31\">PSA 68:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:17\">PRO 13:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:4\">ISA 30:4</a></p>\n<h3>To continue or promote good relations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:1\">1KI 5:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam10:2\">2SA 10:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr19:2\">1CH 19:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:12-2Kgs20:13\">2KI 20:12–20:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa39:1-Isa39:2\">ISA 39:1–39:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:6\">ISA 30:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:9\">ISA 57:9</a> <em>in this instance with godless nations</em></p>\n<h3>To deceive</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh9:4\">JOS 9:4</a></p>\n<h3>To ask for military help</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:4\">2KI 17:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:15\">EZK 17:15</a></p>\n<h3>To make enquiries</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:31\">2CH 32:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:32\">ISA 14:32</a></p>\n<h3>With a message to prepare for war</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa18:2\">ISA 18:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:14\">JER 49:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:1\">OBA 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>To negotiate for peace</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:7\">ISA 33:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:32\">LUK 14:32</a></p>\n<h3>With a message of God's judgment to the nations</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:3\">JER 27:3</a></p>\n<h3>With a message of rebellion</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:14\">LUK 19:14</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are God's envoys to his world</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:20\">2CO 5:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:19\">MAT 28:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:18\">JHN 17:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:21\">JHN 20:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:15\">ROM 10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:7\">ISA 52:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:17\">2CO 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:20\">EPH 6:20</a></p>",
